{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_02_02",
  "title": "成宮すず 2話 たまには息抜き",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "浮き輪の可愛さをもっとアピールして……\nポーズはこんな感じでどうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Show off the cuteness of the pool float more…\nIs this pose good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.833333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、私の優雅な浮き輪姿を\nしっかりとレンズに収めてくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now get my graceful floating pose\nframed just right in the lens.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "海に来て浮かれてるんじゃないかと心配だったが\n撮影には真面目に取り組んでるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was worried you’d reach the beach and get too excited‚\nbut you seem to be taking this shoot very seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ、私は仕事で手を抜いたりしませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I am. I never slack off when I’m working.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "やるからには最高のMVにしてみせますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’m doing it‚ I’m going to make it the best video!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "自信満々な態度がすずらしいな\n堂々としている姿はカメラ映えするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That self-confident attitude is just like you‚ Suzu.\nThat confident look will be photogenic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしょう。この成宮すず、決める時は\nバッチリ決めてみせるのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? When I‚ Suzu Narumiya‚ decide to do something‚\nI show people that I do it perfectly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "張り切って撮影を続けますわよ\n綺麗に撮って下さいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll carry on the shoot with all my energy.\nNow film me in a pretty way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "やっと撮影も一区切りつきましたわね\nここからは遊びますわよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At last‚ a break in filming.\nNow I’m going to play!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの撮影で使った浮き輪\nあれを使って遊んでもよろしいですわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t mind if I play with the\ninflatable I was filmed with earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ダメに決まってるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course you can’t.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "む……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ撮影の小道具ですから仕方がありませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I suppose that makes sense‚ as it’s a video prop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "では{user}さん\n私の荷物からシャチの浮き輪を出してもらえるかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ {user}-san‚\nwould you please bring the orca-shaped pool float from my bag?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "遊ぶのがダメだって言ってるんだ\nこの後も映像の撮り直しがあるかもしれないんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was saying‚ you can't play.\nYou might have to reshoot some of the video later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　せっかくの海なのに！\n遊んじゃダメだなんて意地悪なのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m already here‚ right by the sea!\nSaying I can’t play is just mean!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お願いだからわがままを言わず、我慢してくれよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh please‚ stop being selfish and just put up with it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "嫌ですわ！　私は今すぐ海で遊びたいんですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! I want to play in the sea this minute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "ビーチバレーをするのですわ！\nスイカ割りもするのですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to play some beach volleyball.\nAnd I’m going to play “watermelon splitting!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "駄々をこねるんじゃない\nここへは仕事で来てるんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t get into a tantrum about it.\nYou came here to work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "仕事仕事って……\n毎日そればっかりで気が休まる暇もないんですの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Work work…\nWork all day every day‚ I never have a moment to take it easy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "忙しくても文句を言わず頑張ってきたでしょう？\n今日一日ぐらい好きにさせてほしいのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when I’m really busy‚ I tough it out without complaining‚ don’t I?\nI only want you to let me do what I like‚ just for today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、すずは割と文句を言ってたような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I seem to remember you complaining a lot‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "東京に出て来てからずっと忙しかったんですのよ！\n私だってたまには息抜きしたいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been busy non-stop since I came to Tokyo!\nI just need to take a breather sometimes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに……今日はみんなと海で遊べると思って\nグッズも用意したのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead… I thought I’d be able to play in the sea with everyone today.\nI got all the gear ready…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_02_02-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "それがわがままだなんて……\n私はただ、夏の海を楽しみたかっただけなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you call that being selfish…\nAll I wanted was to enjoy the sea in the summertime…",
